    "causal_summary": "`runRegistryShellRules` filters the validator registry with `rule.strictonly !== true` unconditionally (`orchestrator.ts:269` at time of writing), so strict-only shell rules such as `CONTINUITYFRESHNESS` and `EVIDENCEMARKERLINT` never execute through the default Node path even under `--strict` — while the legacy shell path runs them",
